5: Hello, Alk. Are you out for a walk?
9:
Oh, hi, Junko. And Ai? I... didn't
recognize you right away.
13:
Looks like our disguises are working
spectacularly.
15:
Both of us are off today, so we
decided to head out into town
wearing disguises.
17:
But we're not quite sure exactly
where to go.
19:
Would you two mind joining us for
the day?
21:
We don't know much about this
area, so we'd love to get some
recommendations from you, if
possible.
26:
Oh, but we wouldn't want to bother
you—
31:
We don't have anything particular
on our agenda today, so if it's what
you wish we'll gladly accompany
you.
40:
In this area, I suppose I would have
to recommend—
44:
How about here? You could go on a
sightseeing tour around Saga while
relaxing on a boat.
48:
Now that you mention it, we really
haven't had much of an opportunity
to take in the sights in this new Saga.
53:
Sounds like a good idea to me. Let's
go!
57:
There are larger-sized boats as well,
so all of us can ride—
62:
No, I think we should ride in separate
boats, two people per boat. That
way they can go at their own pace.
65:
Hmm? What's the matter, Alk? The
larger boat would no doubt be more
cost-efficient for us all—
68:
Nope, don't worry about it! Let's just
go!
72:
What exactly was the point of going
out of our way to ride separately, I
wonder?
76:
Don't you worry about that. Row,
row, row your boat, Light!
80:
It's been quite a while since we've
been able to relax like this.
82:
We've been in a constant rush since
we ended up in this new Saga, with
no time to rest.
86:
Yep. And even when we were alive,
we were also busy with idol work.
88:
And after we became zombies,
there was certainly no way we could
wander around outside for a
leisurely stroll.
92:
If you think about it like that, then
perhaps coming to this Saga was a
blessing after all.
95:
Oh? That's a surprisingly optimistic
outlook, despite our rather difficult
situation.
98:
Being part of Franchouchou is what
gives me that optimism, I think.
102:
Well then. Let's ask Alk to show us
around to a whole bunch of places!
104:
And let's make up for all that time
we spent working by having a blast
today!
113:
Wow. To think that such a place
existed so close to where we usually
are...
115:
This is the perfect place for a walk to
clear your mind.
119:
If you go that way, there's actually
an obstacle course too!
123:
Ooh, that sounds cool. I kind of want
to go try it out!
128:
Hmm, then why not make a
competition out of it? Alk and I
versus—
133:
Light! Let's just relax and watch from
a distance.
137:
Um, what exactly does this Pore
flavored ice cream taste like?
141:
Ah, it's hard to describe... It's got kind
of an elastic texture?
145:
I know vanilla, but I've never even
heard of half of these other flavors!
148:
Let's be adventurous and try a flavor
we've never had before.
150:
New experiences like this should
help make us more interesting as
people—and idols.
154:
Not everything we do needs to be
for our brand... But, hey, why not!
Let's do it.
160:
Well, that was a fun day! Thanks for
coming out, everyone.
164:
We had a great day off thanks to
you two.
168:
Well, if it helped you get your minds
off work, I'm happy to have been of
help!
172:
Now that I think about it, we haven't
really had much chance to all go
out together, have we?
176:
If you don't mind, could we take a
photo together? As a memento.
178:
I can't remember the last time I took
a picture that wasn't for work. I'd like
to have one with everyone here.
182:
If it's a souvenir of your trip, maybe it
should just be you two in the picture!
185: No, let's take it with everyone.
189:
Really? Well, if you insist. Excuse me,
could we get our picture taken?
196: Let's do a pose or something!
200:
Hmm... How about this? It's a bit
embarrassing, but why not!
203: Okay, here we go! Say cheese!
206:
Oh, that turned out well. Everyone's
smiling!
210:
I had a great time today, not as an
idol, but as myself.
213:
I feel reinvigorated and ready to
perform again.
215:
The next time I stand on the stage, I'll
channel all the positive energy you
gave me today, and be an even
better idol!
